<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>비밀번호 재설정</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/login/account.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="page">
    <div class="box">

        <div class="logo-area">
            <h1>스마트 약상자</h1>
            <p>나에게 알맞은 약상자 케어 시스템</p>
        </div>

        <div class="pill-icon">🔒</div>

        <h2 class="page-title">비밀번호 재설정</h2>

        <form action="/resetPw" method="post">

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>아이디</label>
                <input type="text" name="id" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>이메일</label>
                <input type="email" name="email" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label>새 비밀번호</label>
                <input type="password" name="newPw" required>
            </div>

            <button class="submit-btn">
                비밀번호 변경
            </button>

        </form>

        <div class="bottom-link">
            <a href="/login">로그인으로 돌아가기</a>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>